      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "The Mother of All Medicines!?",
        "Client": "Prolific Apothecary",
        "Description": "I\u0027ve learned my trade by walking\r\nhill and dale gathering ingredients\r\nfor decades. Mix Tobi-Kadachi\r\nneedles, Rathian spikes, and\r\nHermitaur shell together to stop\r\nbug bite itches! Ouch, they got\r\nme again!",
        "Target": "Hunt all target monsters",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Le meilleur rem\u00E8de ?",
        "Client": "Apothicaire prolifique",
        "Description": "Depuis des d\u00E9cennies, je parcours\r\nle pays \u00E0 la recherche d\u0027ingr\u00E9dients.\r\nIl suffit de m\u00E9langer des aiguilles\r\nde Tobi-Kadachi, des pointes\r\nde Rathian et une carapace\r\nd\u0027Hermitaur pour gu\u00E9rir\r\nles piq\u00FBres d\u0027insecte. Zut, rat\u00E9 !",
        "Target": "Chasser tous les monstres",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "La madre di tutte le medicine?",
        "Client": "Speziale prolifico",
        "Description": "Ho imparato il mio mestiere\r\ncamminando per valli e monti\r\na raccogliere ingredienti per\r\ndecenni. Mescola aculei di\r\nTobi-Kadachi, punte di Rathian\r\ne corazze di Hermitaur contro\r\nil prurito da punture d\u0027insetto.",
        "Target": "Caccia tutti i mostri assegnati",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Die Mutter aller Medizin?!",
        "Client": "Produktiver Apotheker",
        "Description": "Ich habe mein Handwerk gelernt,\r\nindem ich seit Jahrzehnten auf\r\nBergen und in T\u00E4lern Zutaten\r\nsammelte. Mische Tobi-Kadachi-\r\nNadeln, Rathian-Stacheln und\r\nHermitauren-Panzer gegen K\u00E4fer-\r\nbisse! Autsch \u2013 wieder einer!",
